Download the tar file

extract it using> tar -zxvf eclipse.XX.YY.tar.gz

move the file to /opt> sudo mv eclipse.XX.YY /opt

create a desktop icon install> sudo apt-get install --no-install-recommends gnome-panel

goto desktop> gnome-desktop-item-edit --create-new ~/Desktop

A launcher will appear> Type the following things
#!/usr/bin/env xdg-open
[Desktop Entry]
Version=1.0
Type=Application
Terminal=false
Icon[en_IN]=/opt/eclipse-installer/icon.xpm
Name[en_IN]=Eclipse IDE
Comment[en_IN]=IDE
Exec=/opt/eclipse-installer/eclipse-inst
Name=Eclipse IDE
Comment=IDE
Icon=/opt/eclipse-installer/icon.xpm
